snippet.title: Yeah Jam Fury - The Original Trailer!
snippet.description:
Blast from the past! Check out the original advertisement for the fun and fancy free flash game, Yeah Jam Fury!

Still got Flash? Head over to Newgrounds.com to get your fill!
https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/598250

Hungry for more? Head to Steam when Yeah Jam Fury: U, Me, Everybody! launches in December 2017!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/633930/Yeah_Jam_Fury_U_Me_Everybody/
https://wes-plus.com/yeahjamfury/
